  "texts": [
    "Moreover, in training the five models above, seven features are used as predictor variables.",
    "In other settings of applied machine learning, the number of predictor variables can be much larger and that can be an additional source of variation to a prediction task.",
    "Further analysis of data with a much larger set of feature variables can potentially bring additional insights to the complex interplay of data, model and model evaluation metrics.",
    "Regarding the implications for different domains or types of data, no definite answer can be given at this point.",
    "However, we expect similar results to hold in settings with a much large sample size and a lot more feature variables."
